data.description: PRICE ADJUSTMENT . . .  Welcome to this stunning former Casa Real, 1980 SQ FT Model Home located in the gated community of Las Campanas Village. You will find this gorgeous architectural feature of a stone facade. Stepping into the foyer with impressive twelve foot high ceilings. Now glace into the two front rooms with coffer ceilings and crown molding that could be formal dining, living room, music, den or office space.  Spacious kitchen features New 2022 Stainless steel appliances, lots of custom cabinets with under counter cabinet lighting, walk in pantry, Butler's pantry and a very large island allows you to entertain family and friends. The Great Room shows off a 12 foot sliding glass door providing tons of natural light, impressive wood burning fireplace with surrounding built in niches for your choice of art pieces and favorite books.  Sound system with amplifier, adjustable in every room . . . even the patio for your listing pleasure. Stepping outside you will enjoy a large covered patio that extends the interior living area to a very private space to enjoy . . . a cup of coffee, a good book or favorite friends.  Sophisticated Primary En Suite with bay window, coffer ceiling, walk in closet and a new larger step in tile shower or just soak in the garden tub. Split bedroom plan offers guests privacy for a relaxing visit to sunny Arizona. Two car attached garage with a wall of cabinets and utility sink. LCV is a place where you've always belonged  . . . CAREFREE LIVING, welcoming neighbors and social activities.  HOA COVERS: Roof, Stucco, Landscape and Irrigation, Street and Common Area Maintenance, Trash Pick Up, Cable, Pest Control, Structural Hazard Insurance.  NEW ROOF 2023.  Some furnishings available by Seller Bill of Sale.
